===================
Build instructions.
===================

Prequisites:

* Python 2.7+ (CPython/PyPy/Jython)
* Apache Ant 1.8+
* Scala 2.9.0 distribution
* json.simple 1.1 (json_simple-1.1.jar)
* Apache Commons IO 2.0.1 (commons-io-2.0.1.jar)
* Jython minimal library (jython.jar) [for Jython-based plug-in support]
* Groovy library 1.8.0 (groovy-all-1.8.0.jar) [for Groovy-based plug-in support]
* java-gnome 4.0 (gtk-4.0.jar) [for Gnome/Xfce deskop notification suppport]


Steps:

Run on shell, under Gaudi root folder, the following *: 

$ ./configure.py
$ ant
$ sudo ant install
$ ant clean

* Show here using *nix notation. $ is the prompt.

On Windows leave off "./" for configure.py
to use default Python interpreter.
